    <description>Tutanota is the world's most secure email service, easy to use and private by design. Sign up for free encrypted email now.

With end-to-end encryption and 2FA, your emails have never been more secure. The built-in encryption guarantees that your mailbox belongs to you: Nobody can decrypt or read your data.

**Please Note**: This is an automatically updated package. If you find it is out of date by more than a day or two, please contact the maintainer(s) and let them know the package is no longer updating correctly.</description>
    <summary>Tutanota is an email client with a strong focus on security and privacy that lets you encrypt emails on all your devices.</summary>
    <releaseNotes># What's new
 - Expand folder when dragging mail [#10796](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10796)
 - Show failed-to-delete orphaned custom folders [#10836](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10836)

# Bugfixes
 - Error when clicking on elements in mail editor with an id that has the word "align" [#10826](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10826)
 - Can't use email import feature [#10818](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10818)
 - Use appropriate label for showQuickActionBar shortcut [#10865](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10865)
 - creating inbox rules through clicking on to,bcc,sender etc. does not autofill value [#10605](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10605)
 - Squeezed image rendering in some html mails, when max-width: 100% css property is set [#8957](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/8957)
 - Mail opened from notification is re-opened after being moved [#10828](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10828)

# Milestone
https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/milestone/433?closed=1


